Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Shoppes at Grand Prairie’s skill will let you know all the important information and happenings at the center. Whether you’re curious what type of stores they have, where to get a rideshare, when they will be closing, or what the next upcoming event is, download this skill to be informed on all things at The Shoppes at Grand Prairie. You can access this skill on any of your Alexa devices.

To get started, enable The Shoppes at Grand Prairie’s skill through the Alexa App or by saying, “Alexa, open The Shoppes at Grand Prairie.”

If you’re having trouble, please visit www.shoppesatgrandprairie.com.
